public class InvertedIndexList
extends java.util.HashSet<InvertedIndexItem>

InvertedIndexList implementation.

This class is a customized version of a normal Java HashSet that stores InvertedIndexItem objects. Our customizations incldue the ability to use the .contains method regardless of Relationship type and then to simply replace Concept items with new ones.

Author:
kurtisthompson
